name: William Foley
text: If half a star was an option, I would've put that. The food was good, but the staff were rude and clueless. It's like walking into a place and getting the feeling that everyone there hates their jobs. Never buying another thing at this location again.  Absolutely horrible.

name: Joey Manzo
text: Sub was very good but service sucked and took a bit of time.

name: Andrew Brown
text: Great hot sandwich but will have to pay a premium for eating inside of a mall food court.

name: Shraddheya Pathak
text: Tasty sandwiches but a little costly!
